# Schema files

When using Edge Management to deploy adapters onto remotely located devices... <!-- add info about schema file usage -->

Full schema definitions for different facets of each component are available in one of the following folders:

**Windows**
```bash
%ProgramFiles%\OSIsoft\Adapters\<AdapterName>\Schemas
```

**Linux**
```bash
/opt/OSIsoft/Adapters/<AdapterName>/Schemas
```
